Template.Name: ARC_PreAssignment
Template.Description: American Red Cross Pre-Assignment Health Questionnaire

Field.Name: Label1
Field.PromptText: This form is to be filled out by the person at the unit of affiliation that is responsible for DSHR deployment or their designee. If the unit should not have deployed the member based on their DSHR record, they may be charged for the member’s travel.

Field.Name: MemberName
Field.PromptText: Member Name

Field.Name: American
Field.PromptText: American Red Cross

Field.Name: TITLE
Field.PromptText: PRE-ASSIGNMENT HEALTH QUESTIONNAIRE

Field.Name: Requestedfor
Field.PromptText: Requested for DR#

Field.Name: N1label
Field.PromptText: 1 Does the member have a current Health Status Record on file?

Field.Name: N1label2
Field.PromptText: If no, have member complete Health Status Record before continuing.

Field.Name: N2label
Field.PromptText: 2 Does the member have a medical restriction (RM) on their DSHR profile?

Field.Name: N2label2
Field.PromptText: If yes, do not recruit. The RM needs to be resolved first.

Field.Name: N3label
Field.PromptText: 3 Verify any hardship codes associated with the relief operation. Does the member’s DSHR record include any of the hardship codes associated with this relief operation?

Field.Name: N3label2
Field.PromptText: If yes, do not recruit without clearance from the Chapter Health Reviewer. If the chapter does not have a Health Reviewer, the Division Health Consultant must be notified to review the information prior to assignment and deployment.

Field.Name: LabelPart2
Field.PromptText: Read the following statements to the member: “Do not give me any health information. Give me yes or no answers. If you fail to give accurate information and are not able to serve as recruited on the relief operation for health reasons, the Red Cross may request reimbursement for your travel.”

Field.Name: N1labelb
Field.PromptText: 1 Are there any requirements for your group/activity/position on the Physical Capacity Grid that you cannot meet? (Chapter recruiters may need to read the requirements to the member).

Field.Name: N2labelb
Field.PromptText: 2 Do you currently have any stitches or areas of broken skin?

Field.Name: N3labelb
Field.PromptText: 3 Do you currently have a cast, brace or other device that restricts movement?

Field.Name: N4labelb
Field.PromptText: 4 Do you currently use a cane or other device to assist you?

Field.Name: N5labelb
Field.PromptText: 5 Have you been hospitalized or seen in the ER in the past six months?

Field.Name: N6Iableb
Field.PromptText: 6 In the past three days, have you had any symptoms of illness such as fever >100 degrees, cough, sore throat, diarrhea, headache, flu –like symptoms etc.?

Field.Name: N7labelb
Field.PromptText: 7 Has anyone in your immediate family had the flu or flu like symptoms (fever >100 degrees, cough, sore throat, diarrhea, headache within the past 7 days?

Field.Name: N8labelb
Field.PromptText: 8 Have you been around anyone with the flu or flu like symptoms (fever >100 degrees, cough, sore throat, diarrhea, headache in the past 7 days?

Field.Name: N9labelb
Field.PromptText: 9 Have you traveled outside of your normal commuting area in the past 10 days?

Field.Name: N10labelb
Field.PromptText: 10 Do you have any medical/laboratory tests scheduled within the next month?

Field.Name: N11labelb
Field.PromptText: 11 Have you started, changed or stopped any medications in the past 14 days?

Field.Name: N12labelb
Field.PromptText: 12 Will you need to refill any prescriptions during your assignment?

Field.Name: labelc
Field.PromptText: If there are any “Yes” answers to these questions, the member must be approved by the Health Reviewer before deployment.

Field.Name: RecorderName
Field.PromptText: Name of person obtaining information

Field.Name: NameReviewer
Field.PromptText: Name of Health Reviewer given the “yes” information above

Field.Name: labeld
Field.PromptText: Retain this form in the member’s DSHR file in case it is requested by Staff Health at national headquarters, the Division Staff Health Consultant or Staff Health on the relief operation.

Field.Name: Rev409
Field.PromptText: Rev 4/09
